  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went first to this church.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and of course, we knew-- I have seen those guys watching me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were also in the church, in church, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after the church, I took him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to-- to the river, to the shore of the river, where one-- where the boats to-- to rent.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we rented a boat, and we went for-- you know, a ride on-- on the boat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because in this town, there was quite a large river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after that-- so when we went to the boat, this-- this guy who was watching us in church, he could not go because he-- he was doing it secretly.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he went back home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we went on the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after an hour-- because we know that at 3 o'clock, there will be freight train going through the city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And usually, you know, in the eastern of Poland, all these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] train tracks were outside of the cities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the policy of the Russian government because this region was under Russian-- under Russian before World War I.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the railroad was quite a distance from the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not in the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we know that at 3 o'clock, there is always every day a-- a freight train going toward Warsaw-- toward Lemberg, toward Lublin-- Lwow, and Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So after this rowing the boat, we left the-- the boat at the-- you know, back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and through-- through the fields, we went to-- close to the railroad, and we waited in bushes until we hear the rail-- the trains coming.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And apparently, this place, there was a hill.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
